OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a grey and often wet
OL,6,Fstart to the day across Wales,
OL,7,Fparticularly across the northwest.
OL,8,FHowever, rain will gradually ease,
OL,9,Fwith most areas seeing a dry afternoon
OL,10,Fwith some warm bright or sunny spells
OL,11,Fdeveloping.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA clear and dry night to
OL,14,Fstart. Low cloud moving into the west
OL,15,Fduring the early hours which could
OL,16,Fbring a spot of rain. Staying very
OL,17,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
