OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLow cloud in the west will
OL,6,Flift through the morning, leaving a
OL,7,Fdry and bright day for most, with warm
OL,8,Fhazy sunshine. Temperatures continue
OL,9,Fto rise above the May average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FVery
OL,12,Fwarm over the Bank Holiday weekend
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunshine and light
OL,14,Fwinds. Any early morning cloud should
OL,15,Fburn back to the coasts through the
OL,16,Fmorning each day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
